<div class="contextual-help-item principal-help" i18n:domain="novaideo">
	<p i18n:translate="">In order to explain each of your improvements, you can click on the related number.</p>

	<p i18n:translate="">You can either re-use the existing explanation of an earlier improvement, or give a specific one. If you modify an existing explanation, this change in the explanation will be replicated to all improvements that share this explanation. If you wish to modify a single explanation only, you must provide a specific explanation.</p>

	<p i18n:translate="">You can also relate an idea to an explanation or write down a new idea.</p>

	<p i18n:translate="">If you wish to split an improvement in several parts, you can integrate additional improvements to the text.</p>
</div>